``polars sort-by``
[link: /commands/categories/lazyframe.md] ’Щ@e658320ed9b9cf2e2f9812db93da26a8a965bd5042cc254aa0cdf766fbf06cb2Щ[Title: title: polars sort-by
Path: Signature
Content:
``> polars sort-by {flags} ...rest``
’Щ@1f9abc26ff75d98052dd0944e268bbdf7ff67b16273b5299bcac25acbbf9cdf7ЩмTitle: title: polars sort-by
Path: Flags
Content:
``--reverse, -r {list<bool>}``
: Reverse sorting. Default is false.
``--nulls-last, -n``
: Nulls are shown last in the dataframe.
``--maintain-order, -m``
: Maintains order during sort.
’Щ@73f14d462bb86c8051a2ee6855c198e3f57ffc35e8df84faea9d9dd66847d7b6ЩhTitle: title: polars sort-by
Path: Parameters
Content:
``...rest``
: Sort expression for the dataframe.
